# Email Registration API Example

POST /register
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "email": "user@email.com",
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "age": 30,
  "sex": "female"
}

# Certificate API Example

POST /certificate
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "email": "user@email.com",
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "finishTime": "1:23:45",
  "globalRank": 42,
  "ageSexRank": 5
}
